These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, balloon-flower, daisy
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, drama, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, tennis, golf, sailing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dannemann, game, baccarat
City: hannover, colone, liverpool, paris
 1. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who growsiris and the person traveling to paris##2
 3. the davidoff-smoker is the person traveling to paris##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 5. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who growsiris and the person who's sport is golf##2
 6. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | iris   | daisy | orchid |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | disaster | drama              | superhero |
| Sport   | basketball       | tennis     | sailing               | golf    |
| Cigar           | dannemann        | game     | baccarat           | davidoff       |
| City     | colone | liverpool     | hannover                | paris      |

