.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, fuchsia, blood-red, light-blue
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, june, december
City: rome, berlin, hannover, colone
House: cottage, palace, craftsman, colonial
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who likes blood-red and the palace house##2
 4. the person traveling to colone is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the craftsman house is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the colonial house##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person who likes blood-red##1
12. the person who likes lilac is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Color          | blood-red       | fuchsia      | lilac      | light-blue      |
| Birthday           | december | january | june | september |
