.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid, zinnia, azalea
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, car, quad-bike
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, tea, sprite
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, horse, mouse
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, canasta, chess
 1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person driving the skateboard and the person playing backgammon##2
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person drinking juice is the owner of the mouse##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Flower          | orchid    | daffodil  | azalea | zinnia |
| Transport   | taxi   | car        | skateboard | quad-bike     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | juice    | sprite  | tea   |
| Pet           | horse     | mouse      | chinchilla | dog        |
| Game         | backgammon      | chess | scrabble      | canasta     |

