The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, parkour, snowboarding, soccer
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, white, turquise
 1. the person who likes white is the person who growsdaisy##1
 2. the person who likes emerald is between the dunhill-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##2
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the colonial house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who likes ivory##2
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 8. the cottage house is the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the ranch-style house is between the person who likes emerald and the pall-mall-smoker##2
10. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| House      | gothic-revival     | ranch-style | colonial    | cottage          |
| Flower          | sunflower | daisy     | orchid | dahlia         |
