 7. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person drinking iced-tea##2
11. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
