 8. the fan of trance is between the fan of d&b and the person who growsrose##2
 9. the person playing go is on the far left##1
10. the person playing canasta is between the person who growsrose and the person playing scrabble##2
11. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
