4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, game, old-henry, bluemaster
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, malaysian, dutch
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, rose, sunflower, balloon-flower
City: san-francisco, liverpool, marseilles, nizza
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, subway, taxi
 1. the chinese is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person who growsrose and the person driving the subway##2
 3. the person who growssunflower is between the bluemaster-smoker and the game-smoker##2
 4. the person driving the roller is the pakistani##1
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is the dutch##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is between the dutch and the person driving the taxi##2
12. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person driving the roller and the chaman-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | game      | chaman         | bluemaster | old-henry      |
| Nationality           | dutch | malaysian | chinese | pakistani     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower         | sunflower          | bellflower  | rose |
| City         | marseilles        | nizza  | liverpool | san-francisco   |
| Transport     | skateboard    | subway         | taxi     | roller     |

