.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, chess, video-games, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, d&b, house, techno
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, december, june
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, social-worker, designer, scientist
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, subway, trike
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the designer and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 3. the social-worker is the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
 5. the scientist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of techno##1
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of house##1
10. the scientist is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the fan of techno and the paramedic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
