4 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, rat, lizard
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, chestnut, black, coral
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, scooter, van
 1. the owner of the rat is the person watching drama movies##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is between the person who likes coral and the owner of the lizard##2
 4. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes purple##1
 5. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to venice and the person driving the van##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the person who likes black is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
