The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, august, april
4 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, snake, fish
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, ship
 1. the person watching animation movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person driving the ship is between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the bird##2
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the owner of the rabbit and the person driving the roller##2
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
